  m_Name: Faces For Sale
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Title: Faces for Sale
  Description: 'The main commodity of the store is dice faces. Buying a new face
    will replace the visible face of the die in the middle of the shop.


    Buying
    faces could help you increase your odds of rolling a certain number, so use that
    wisely.


    But remember, spending points too recklessly will make it harder
    to pay the next installment!'
